text: The 1966 Soviet Class A Second Group was the fourth season of the Soviet Class A Second Group football competitions that was established in 1963. It was also the 26th season of the Soviet second tier league competition. ==First stage== ===First subgroup=== ===Second subgroup=== ===Third subgroup=== ==Final stage== ===For places 1-3=== [Oct 25 – Nov 16] ===For places 4-6=== [Oct 29 – Nov 14] ==See also== * Soviet First League ==External links== * 1966 season.
